WEBVTT

00:46.045 --> 00:49.424
LEE YEO-REUM

02:18.429 --> 02:21.057
ANGOK PUBLIC LIBRARY

03:04.267 --> 03:07.145
CHECKOUT, RETURN

03:17.947 --> 03:22.285
LITERATURE

03:39.594 --> 03:41.387
THE OLD MAN AND THE SEA

03:49.938 --> 03:52.690
"Men are not created with defeat in mind."

03:54.275 --> 03:58.154
"We may fall at times
but we're never defeated."

04:04.035 --> 04:06.788
All right. I'll live here.

04:17.507 --> 04:18.383
Excuse me.

04:28.643 --> 04:29.852
Excuse me, Miss.

04:34.232 --> 04:36.693
Where's the real estate agency
around here?

04:46.077 --> 04:47.370
I'm sorry.

04:48.955 --> 04:50.123
I'm sorry.

05:01.592 --> 05:02.719
Hey.

05:02.802 --> 05:05.388
-Hey, pass it here!
-No!

05:08.349 --> 05:09.767
-You over there!
-Hey!

05:09.851 --> 05:11.728
-Old lady with the bag! Pass the ball!
-Pass it!

05:11.811 --> 05:13.479
-Over here!
-The ball!

05:13.563 --> 05:14.439
Me?

05:14.522 --> 05:16.065
-You're the only one there.
-Hurry up.

05:16.149 --> 05:17.775
-Roll the ball over here.
-Roll it.

05:17.859 --> 05:18.901
Hurry up.

05:18.985 --> 05:20.236
-Give us our ball.
-Hey.

05:20.320 --> 05:22.572
-Hurry.
-I'm not an old lady!

05:32.957 --> 05:34.834
-Hey, Dae-bum!
-Dae-bum!

05:34.917 --> 05:36.002
Hey!

05:36.085 --> 05:38.337
-Dae-bum, look at me.
-Are you okay?

05:38.421 --> 05:39.464
-Is your head okay?
-Are you okay?

05:39.547 --> 05:40.840
-Are you okay?
-Look at me!

05:40.923 --> 05:42.258
-Look at his face.
-Goodness.

05:42.341 --> 05:44.302
-I'm so sorry.
-Dae-bum!

05:44.385 --> 05:45.595
-Hey, you!
-Oh, no.

05:45.678 --> 05:47.221
-Hey!
-Do you want to die?

05:47.305 --> 05:48.931
-How can you do this to Dae-bum?
-What is this?

05:49.015 --> 05:49.932
-Go away!
-You're dead meat.

05:50.016 --> 05:52.185
-How dare you?
-Go away!

05:52.268 --> 05:53.895
-I'm sorry.
-Get out of here!

05:53.978 --> 05:55.396
-I'm so sorry.
-Go away!

05:55.480 --> 05:56.856
-Go!
-Don't come back here!

06:03.237 --> 06:05.031
JEONG HAIR SALON, ALTTEUL STORE,
ANGOK REAL ESTATE, ANGOK LIBRARY

06:05.615 --> 06:06.866
It's a map.

06:16.000 --> 06:18.044
I told you it's fine.

06:18.127 --> 06:21.255
Tell them I got your back
if you see those thugs again.

06:21.339 --> 06:23.174
Bae Seong-min,
the youth wrestling bronze medalist.

06:23.257 --> 06:24.759
-I'm going now.
-Hold on.

06:24.842 --> 06:26.052
-Hey, stop.
-Listen.

06:26.135 --> 06:27.220
Hey!

06:27.303 --> 06:28.137
My back!

06:28.221 --> 06:30.556
Goodness.

06:30.640 --> 06:31.724
Wait.

06:32.350 --> 06:33.392
My back.

06:33.476 --> 06:35.853
-Massage my back.
-You're on my legs, man.

06:37.105 --> 06:38.231
Excuse me.

06:40.525 --> 06:43.152
Do you sell superglue?

06:43.236 --> 06:45.279
Check where the paintbrushes are.

06:45.363 --> 06:47.657
Goodness. Are you okay?

06:48.491 --> 06:49.951
You should be more careful.

06:50.535 --> 06:51.869
This hurts so bad.

06:52.370 --> 06:54.247
It's been so long since I've done that.

06:54.330 --> 06:55.373
Man, my back.

06:57.250 --> 06:59.752
I went a little overboard.

07:17.937 --> 07:19.647
-Excuse me.
-Yes?

07:21.816 --> 07:23.359
The glue is 2,000 won.

07:23.443 --> 07:25.778
-Actually…
-What is it?

07:25.862 --> 07:27.363
Where are you going, Bom?

07:27.864 --> 07:29.574
I'm leaving because all your stuff sucks.

07:30.283 --> 07:31.284
That brat.

07:31.367 --> 07:33.578
Why does she come here
if she's not buying anything?

07:33.661 --> 07:35.455
Like I said, this is 2,000 won.

07:35.538 --> 07:36.789
Okay.

07:38.624 --> 07:39.959
Is your back okay?

07:40.042 --> 07:41.544
-Here you go.
-Thanks.

07:42.670 --> 07:43.629
Goodbye.

07:45.214 --> 07:46.966
-Have a good day.
-Sure.

07:51.345 --> 07:52.221
Busted.

07:53.014 --> 07:53.848
Come over here.

08:05.234 --> 08:07.028
-Pass it over here!
-Hey.

08:07.111 --> 08:09.113
Go hang out somewhere else, you punks!

08:09.197 --> 08:11.741
You're dead meat if you hit my car.

08:12.325 --> 08:13.326
Get out of here!

08:14.494 --> 08:15.536
Darn it.

08:21.584 --> 08:23.127
There's no one here, right?

08:36.557 --> 08:39.018
Just how much longer
do I have to stay here in Angok?

08:39.602 --> 08:42.897
Why won't they transfer me out of here?

08:42.980 --> 08:45.483
They screwed me over again, Dae-bum.

08:45.566 --> 08:47.401
I won't make it into
the district office this time either.

08:49.570 --> 08:50.780
I'm so irritated.

08:50.863 --> 08:53.366
Why are they doing this to me?

08:55.660 --> 08:58.329
I want to go to Seoul.

08:58.955 --> 09:00.915
I hate Angok!

09:09.006 --> 09:10.299
Whatever.

09:10.967 --> 09:12.343
I'm so sick of this place.

09:13.344 --> 09:15.346
I only bought the superglue.

09:15.846 --> 09:19.225
We'll see about that
when I empty out your bag.

09:19.308 --> 09:20.268
What's this?

09:20.851 --> 09:23.145
Who carries their blanket around?

09:23.771 --> 09:25.982
What are you, a traveler?

09:26.065 --> 09:27.066
What's this?

09:31.195 --> 09:32.822
-What about this?
-That's…

09:33.864 --> 09:35.116
-Seong-man.
-Yes?

09:35.741 --> 09:36.784
Pockets.

09:36.867 --> 09:37.952
Check her pockets.

09:40.538 --> 09:42.790
Miss, let me see…

09:43.791 --> 09:45.626
-Let me see your…
-What are you doing?

09:46.294 --> 09:47.420
Let me see your pockets.

09:50.923 --> 09:52.300
There's nothing in here.

09:55.720 --> 09:57.179
This is strange.

09:57.888 --> 10:00.308
I paid a fortune for that alarm.

10:04.353 --> 10:05.479
What's this?

10:08.816 --> 10:10.985
Are you kidding me?

10:11.068 --> 10:13.112
Why would you stick this on there?

10:13.195 --> 10:15.656
I didn't put it on there.

10:16.699 --> 10:18.034
A 4B pencil?

10:19.118 --> 10:20.703
Do we have 4B pencils?

10:22.038 --> 10:25.458
Why would you doubt your customer?

10:29.629 --> 10:32.214
JEONG HAIR SALON, ALTTEUL STORE,
ANGOK REAL ESTATE, ANGOK LIBRARY

10:32.298 --> 10:35.092
Young people these days are so creative.

10:35.176 --> 10:38.596
They often renovate places like this.

10:39.347 --> 10:41.098
The owner is an old lady…

10:41.182 --> 10:42.183
Goodness, be careful.

10:42.266 --> 10:44.018
Does the electricity work?

10:44.101 --> 10:46.312
-Well… What is this?
-Goodness.

10:50.441 --> 10:52.151
How much is the rent here?

10:52.234 --> 10:55.696
It's 500,000 won a month,
but I can negotiate.

10:55.780 --> 10:57.406
The deposit is 20 million won.

11:00.993 --> 11:04.246
The rent is 200,000 won
with a deposit of 2 million won.

11:04.872 --> 11:06.957
But I can get the rent down
to 170,000 won.

11:07.583 --> 11:08.584
I see.

11:08.668 --> 11:10.628
You said the bathroom was outside, right?

11:10.711 --> 11:12.546
The communal bathroom is down here…

11:14.382 --> 11:17.468
What the hell is he scratching?
Did he just smell his hand?

11:19.637 --> 11:21.347
I'm sorry,

11:21.430 --> 11:23.557
but I can't let you live here.

11:23.641 --> 11:26.102
ANGOK REAL ESTATE AGENCY

11:31.357 --> 11:32.525
What a shame.

11:38.364 --> 11:39.657
Excuse me.

11:40.491 --> 11:43.411
This is my wife's idea,

11:43.494 --> 11:45.329
but would you be willing
to see one more place?

11:45.955 --> 11:47.123
Where is it?

11:47.206 --> 11:49.041
It's a bit difficult to describe it.

11:49.125 --> 11:50.876
-Let's go see it for ourselves.
-Okay.

11:56.674 --> 11:58.175
It's this building.

11:59.844 --> 12:01.554
-This isn't a house.
-What?

12:02.179 --> 12:03.264
No, it isn't.

12:04.974 --> 12:06.225
It's not even locked.

12:09.061 --> 12:10.938
-Let's head inside.
-Okay.

12:11.814 --> 12:13.274
Over this way.

12:15.443 --> 12:16.694
Goodness.

12:19.071 --> 12:20.489
Let's see.

12:20.573 --> 12:22.658
Come in this way.

12:23.534 --> 12:28.456
This place used to be
the largest billiard club in the town.

12:28.539 --> 12:30.040
It's so spacious.

12:30.708 --> 12:32.334
You could even play soccer here.

12:34.170 --> 12:38.132
When they were building this place,
they used absurd amounts of cement,

12:38.215 --> 12:40.009
so the building is extremely sturdy.

12:40.092 --> 12:41.093
It'll never collapse.

12:43.429 --> 12:44.513
Right, the rooftop.

12:45.055 --> 12:47.057
Try going up to the rooftop
on a sunny day.

12:47.141 --> 12:48.767
The sunlight is so warm

12:48.851 --> 12:51.103
that your laundry dries nice and crisp.

12:54.064 --> 12:55.149
That's not all.

12:57.234 --> 13:00.988
You can use this whole building.

13:03.032 --> 13:04.742
The entire building?

13:05.618 --> 13:06.702
That's right.

13:08.037 --> 13:10.915
So no one lives here?

13:11.916 --> 13:14.627
Well, so to speak.

13:16.128 --> 13:18.339
I guess it's not the best place
for a young lady.

13:23.969 --> 13:26.889
How much is the rent?

13:27.473 --> 13:29.642
Rent? Do you like it?

13:29.725 --> 13:32.061
My wife was right.

13:32.144 --> 13:34.063
I knew you were a unique one.

13:34.647 --> 13:37.107
In that case, I'll go make an arrangement

13:37.191 --> 13:39.485
with the landowner about the rent.

13:39.568 --> 13:41.654
So please stay here for a second, okay?

13:42.738 --> 13:43.864
Sir.

13:50.329 --> 13:52.122
-Hey.
-Hey.

13:52.206 --> 13:54.208
-I'm here.
-Welcome.

13:56.001 --> 13:58.879
I have something to discuss with you.

13:59.630 --> 14:02.258
Goodness. You shouldn't have.

14:02.883 --> 14:04.426
Gosh.

14:05.427 --> 14:07.263
-What is it?
-So…

14:08.222 --> 14:13.143
I showed a few houses
to a young lady from Seoul today,

14:13.227 --> 14:16.397
and suddenly, you crossed my mind.

14:17.565 --> 14:18.899
Why me?

14:19.984 --> 14:21.068
Well…

14:22.903 --> 14:24.905
What if I showed her that place?

14:25.573 --> 14:26.740
What place?

14:27.241 --> 14:30.160
The first floor isn't great.
So the one above, the billiard club.

14:30.244 --> 14:33.038
I already told Chang-su
that I'd sell it to him.

14:33.706 --> 14:36.208
Plus, the place isn't for housing.

14:37.751 --> 14:41.463
Did she seem like a decent person?

14:41.547 --> 14:43.883
Yes, she seemed very honest.

14:45.050 --> 14:48.846
But still, if she hears rumors
about the place later…

16:08.968 --> 16:12.221
Towns like Yangyang became popular
after young people moved in.

16:12.304 --> 16:16.100
You know how much the rents
and real estate prices went up by.

16:16.183 --> 16:17.351
You little brat.

16:17.434 --> 16:19.728
Why weren't you working at the store?

16:19.812 --> 16:22.606
I was at Chang-su's for a bit.

16:22.690 --> 16:24.316
What brings you here, Mr. Kwak?

16:25.025 --> 16:27.945
I just had something to discuss with him.

16:28.028 --> 16:29.321
ALTTEUL STORE

16:29.405 --> 16:30.614
Seong-man.

16:30.698 --> 16:33.534
I don't think I can sell
that building to Chang-su.

16:34.451 --> 16:35.577
What?

16:35.661 --> 16:39.581
Dad, are you losing it with your old age?

16:40.374 --> 16:43.043
I just talked Chang-su
into buying the building.

16:43.585 --> 16:46.714
He has the down payment ready
to sign the contract this week.

16:46.797 --> 16:49.925
Just like you said,
we haven't signed the contract yet.

16:50.009 --> 16:52.386
I changed my mind.
He'll just have to deal with it.

16:52.469 --> 16:55.014
That's right.
The contract is what legally--

16:55.097 --> 16:56.432
Come on, man!

16:56.515 --> 16:59.268
According to Mr. Kwak over here,

16:59.351 --> 17:01.812
we'd be at a huge loss
selling it for that price.

17:01.895 --> 17:02.980
For goodness' sake.

17:03.063 --> 17:03.897
Dad.

17:03.981 --> 17:06.775
Do you know how many years
that place has been left empty for?

17:06.859 --> 17:10.612
Whatever. Go with Mr. Kwak right now.

17:10.696 --> 17:11.780
What? Where?

17:11.864 --> 17:14.158
Go to the billiard club
and sign the contract.

17:14.742 --> 17:18.078
I need to go into town
to get a new refrigerator.

17:18.162 --> 17:19.830
-What the…
-See you later.

17:19.913 --> 17:22.291
-See you.
-What contract, Dad?

17:29.131 --> 17:31.258
-Who is it?
-Goodness!

17:31.341 --> 17:32.801
Who are you?

17:32.885 --> 17:34.344
-Mr. Kwak?
-Honey.

17:34.428 --> 17:36.805
-Honey, what's wrong?
-Look over there.

17:37.890 --> 17:38.807
Oh, my!

17:38.891 --> 17:41.101
Who are you?

17:41.185 --> 17:43.270
I came to look at the house.

17:43.771 --> 17:44.730
Who are you?

17:44.813 --> 17:47.066
-What?
-You're here to look at the house?

17:47.149 --> 17:48.609
Chang-su!

17:48.692 --> 17:50.527
-Chang-su!
-Seriously?

17:50.611 --> 17:52.488
-What?
-Hey, Seong-man!

17:53.197 --> 17:55.699
You said we can come and take measurements

17:55.783 --> 17:58.077
and you rented it out to someone else?

17:58.160 --> 17:59.787
That's not it.

17:59.870 --> 18:03.123
I just found out as well.
Let's go outside and talk.

18:03.207 --> 18:05.209
We can talk right here.

18:05.292 --> 18:07.586
-We have a guest here, so…
-A guest?

18:07.669 --> 18:09.630
Hey, don't worry about it.

18:09.713 --> 18:10.881
-Let's go outside.
-Hey.

18:10.964 --> 18:12.508
-Let's go outside and talk.
-You…

18:12.591 --> 18:14.343
You little brat.

18:14.426 --> 18:16.845
Trust me this once.

18:16.929 --> 18:19.389
Do you know how many times you lied to us?

18:19.473 --> 18:21.183
-Are you okay?
-Yes.

18:21.809 --> 18:23.268
You must have been startled.

18:23.852 --> 18:27.022
Let's go somewhere brighter
since there are no lights in here.

18:27.856 --> 18:29.775
What's with all the yelling?

18:29.858 --> 18:30.901
Let's go, come on.

18:30.984 --> 18:32.653
Don't push me!

18:32.736 --> 18:33.904
You should read the room.

18:33.987 --> 18:36.198
Don't push me. I can walk on my own.

18:36.281 --> 18:37.741
Who's that lady?

18:37.825 --> 18:40.577
What do you mean she's a guest?

18:41.161 --> 18:43.997
Is your dad selling her the place
for more money?

18:44.706 --> 18:47.584
She's looking to rent the place.

18:47.668 --> 18:49.837
It makes no sense,
so don't even worry about it.

18:49.920 --> 18:54.091
But why would you rent this place out
without our approval?

18:54.174 --> 18:56.510
Do you think that makes sense?

18:56.593 --> 18:59.263
I've never rented this place out.
I don't even want to.

18:59.972 --> 19:02.599
This is all my father's doing.

19:02.683 --> 19:03.767
That's why I said…

19:03.851 --> 19:05.227
Why are they yelling?

19:05.310 --> 19:07.980
All right. If that happens,
I won't hold back either.

19:08.063 --> 19:10.482
Go back to the store
with your wife, Chang-su.

19:10.566 --> 19:13.569
I'll wrap up the situation here
and get back to you.

19:13.652 --> 19:16.530
Seong-man. Do better, okay?

19:16.613 --> 19:19.533
Of course. I'm Bae Seong-min!

19:19.616 --> 19:20.701
What a joke.

19:20.784 --> 19:22.619
You can go in now. Bye.

19:23.203 --> 19:25.414
-For the love of…
-Come on now.

19:25.497 --> 19:27.457
-You won't break it like that.
-See you.

19:28.083 --> 19:31.712
Did I do something wrong, by any chance?

19:31.795 --> 19:34.214
Not at all.

19:34.298 --> 19:37.009
There must have been
some kind of misunderstanding.

19:37.092 --> 19:39.595
No need to concern yourself over it.

19:39.678 --> 19:42.472
Mr. Kwak!

19:43.265 --> 19:47.060
How did you butter up my dad this time?

19:47.144 --> 19:50.439
Come on, we have a guest here.

19:50.522 --> 19:53.150
This is the landlord's son.

19:54.610 --> 19:55.986
Aren't you from Altteul Store?

19:56.069 --> 19:57.362
Lady.

19:57.446 --> 20:00.824
I was an athlete,
so I hate beating around the bush.

20:01.909 --> 20:05.162
Do you even know
what kind of place this is?

20:05.245 --> 20:06.788
-Stop talking.
-Do you?

20:06.872 --> 20:10.209
This place has been vacant for 20 years.
Why do you think that is?

20:10.792 --> 20:12.002
Twenty years?

20:12.085 --> 20:12.961
Come here.

20:13.629 --> 20:17.507
Are you going to be like this?
Your dad already agreed on this.

20:17.591 --> 20:18.884
You said she'll be a tenant.

20:18.967 --> 20:20.219
What is it?

20:20.302 --> 20:21.637
It's nothing.

20:22.137 --> 20:23.931
What do you mean it's nothing?

20:24.514 --> 20:26.058
People died here.

20:26.141 --> 20:27.392
What?

20:27.476 --> 20:29.895
Can you live in a place
where people died? I couldn't.

20:29.978 --> 20:31.980
Are you really going to be like this?

20:32.981 --> 20:35.442
Of course, this is your decision to make,

20:35.525 --> 20:38.070
but nothing happened after that incident.

20:38.153 --> 20:39.279
Mr. Kwak.

20:40.072 --> 20:43.825
Look at her face.
She's totally freaked out.

20:43.909 --> 20:46.203
Let's not talk here in the dark.

20:46.286 --> 20:48.038
Let's talk outside.
There are ghosts in here.

20:48.121 --> 20:49.373
-Let's go.
-You little…

20:49.456 --> 20:52.167
If you keep this up,
I'm going to tell your dad.

20:52.251 --> 20:53.585
Go ahead.

20:54.169 --> 20:56.672
And you have issues too, Mr. Kwak.

20:56.755 --> 20:59.925
Why did you bring her here
when there are perfectly fine houses?

21:00.008 --> 21:02.261
-Are you trying to scam her?
-Miss.

21:02.344 --> 21:03.679
It's 50,000 won.

21:04.263 --> 21:05.389
-Sorry?
-What?

21:05.889 --> 21:08.350
I'll rent it out to you for 50,000 won.

21:08.433 --> 21:09.476
What did you say?

21:09.559 --> 21:10.602
It's 50,000 won?

21:10.686 --> 21:13.814
Why else would I show you
this good-for-nothing property?

21:13.897 --> 21:16.149
Don't be ridiculous, Mr. Kwak.

21:16.233 --> 21:18.860
The landlord agreed
to rent the place out to you

21:18.944 --> 21:21.363
for 50,000 won a month under the condition

21:21.446 --> 21:23.323
that you maintain this place.

21:23.907 --> 21:26.368
So my dad agreed
to rent this place out for 50,000 won?

21:26.451 --> 21:27.869
That's right!

21:27.953 --> 21:29.371
-He did.
-Fine. I'll call him.

21:29.454 --> 21:30.789
Lady, think rationally.

21:30.872 --> 21:32.541
That's 50,000 per month.

21:32.624 --> 21:35.210
If I live here for 12 months,

21:35.294 --> 21:37.212
it'll be 600,000 won.

21:37.796 --> 21:40.132
So what do you want to do?

21:42.467 --> 21:45.137
I'll take it.

21:45.220 --> 21:46.388
What did you say?

21:46.471 --> 21:48.432
You've made a great decision.

21:48.515 --> 21:52.227
-Hello? Dad, I'm at the building.
-Let me pray for you.

21:52.311 --> 21:54.021
-Dear heavenly Father,
-He says the rent is 50,000 won.

21:54.104 --> 21:55.856
This sister has found a new home

21:55.939 --> 21:57.399
-in this building.
-He's right?

21:57.482 --> 21:59.860
-Please bless her with your grace.
-Dad!

21:59.943 --> 22:01.695
-Dad!
-Amen.

22:01.778 --> 22:03.322
This is driving me nuts.

22:03.905 --> 22:05.866
Seong-man! Let's go.

22:06.700 --> 22:08.577
Wait a second.

22:08.660 --> 22:10.871
Have you seen the bathroom here?

22:10.954 --> 22:14.374
Your poop won't flush.
You can't even shower there.

22:14.458 --> 22:16.626
How can you live in this horrible place?

22:16.710 --> 22:18.628
Give it another thought.

22:18.712 --> 22:22.215
LANDLORD: BAE YEONG-HO
TENANT: LEE YEO-REUM

22:23.216 --> 22:25.302
I'm glad you liked the place.

22:25.385 --> 22:26.344
I did.

22:26.928 --> 22:28.680
-Come on.
-In that case,

22:28.764 --> 22:31.183
-you can wire 600,000 won at once.
-Okay.

22:35.228 --> 22:36.396
I transferred it.

22:36.980 --> 22:37.939
Check your account.

22:41.318 --> 22:42.819
What about the commission?

22:42.903 --> 22:45.030
I don't need any. It's fine.

22:46.073 --> 22:47.824
We just want you to be well.

22:47.908 --> 22:49.701
Thank you so much.

22:52.621 --> 22:57.501
Would it be okay if I moved in today?

22:57.584 --> 22:58.835
Today?

22:59.795 --> 23:01.797
But the place doesn't
even have any lights.

23:01.880 --> 23:03.048
It's fine.

23:04.341 --> 23:06.384
The contract is valid starting today, so…

23:06.968 --> 23:09.221
You're so obnoxious.

23:10.055 --> 23:12.140
-Darn it.
-Seong-min.

23:13.433 --> 23:14.935
You have to give her the keys.

23:19.981 --> 23:20.982
Here you go, ma'am.

23:21.066 --> 23:22.776
-Okay?
-Honey.

23:22.859 --> 23:24.778
Can you bring out that thing I mentioned?

23:24.861 --> 23:26.321
Right. Sure.

23:27.572 --> 23:29.616
There are no lights in there.

23:29.699 --> 23:31.284
Thank you.

23:31.368 --> 23:33.328
-Enjoy your new home.
-Thank you.

23:34.287 --> 23:36.123
-He's such a brat.
-Goodbye.

23:36.206 --> 23:38.458
-Good night.
-Goodbye.

23:43.588 --> 23:44.881
Excuse me.

23:45.799 --> 23:49.970
Thank you for telling me the truth
about the place.

23:51.513 --> 23:54.266
I would have freaked out
if I found out later.

23:57.018 --> 23:58.353
Whatever.

23:58.436 --> 24:02.357
If anything breaks,
you can take care of it yourself.

24:02.440 --> 24:04.985
You can always leave
when you can't take it anymore.

24:05.068 --> 24:06.278
Got it?

24:07.445 --> 24:08.488
Okay.

24:21.793 --> 24:23.336
I have a home now.

25:15.055 --> 25:17.265
MY FIRST DAY IN ANGOK

25:17.349 --> 25:20.268
After I quit my job without a plan,

25:21.019 --> 25:24.272
I stayed in bed for two days.

25:25.815 --> 25:27.025
I was afraid.

25:28.485 --> 25:32.614
I had no idea what to do next.

25:38.995 --> 25:41.498
First, I decided to leave Seoul.

25:42.707 --> 25:46.294
Seoul is too much
for an unemployed person like me.

26:00.976 --> 26:05.522
I got rid of Jae-dong's belongings
that I'd been neglecting.

26:10.110 --> 26:13.321
And as for my belongings,

26:13.405 --> 26:15.782
I decided to only keep
what could fit in my backpack.

26:18.618 --> 26:22.872
Cleaning up the house,
I realized that I bought a lot of things.

26:22.956 --> 26:25.750
Mugs that I bought on a whim
just because they were pretty,

26:26.376 --> 26:29.379
dishes that I used only once
to host a housewarming party…

26:33.717 --> 26:36.344
clothes that I forgot existed,

26:37.178 --> 26:40.598
cheap shoes I bought out of habit…

26:42.350 --> 26:46.271
I picked out one from each category
that seemed necessary.

26:47.022 --> 26:50.442
The selection process was more difficult
than my job interviews.

26:51.860 --> 26:55.739
Useless items got sold
as soon as I posted them online.

27:01.453 --> 27:02.495
Goodbye.

27:03.580 --> 27:05.498
My six pyeong life.

27:13.923 --> 27:16.051
I want to find an answer

27:17.135 --> 27:18.762
before this journey ends.

27:20.930 --> 27:24.476
As to how I should live my life
from now on.

27:39.949 --> 27:42.660
ALARM

27:42.744 --> 27:44.371
YOU HAVE NO ALARMS

27:59.469 --> 28:01.346
The sky looks amazing from here.

28:17.946 --> 28:19.280
Welcome.

28:21.991 --> 28:23.201
Hello.

28:25.578 --> 28:27.247
How can I help you?

28:27.330 --> 28:31.042
How do I make a library card here?

28:32.377 --> 28:34.963
You need an address in Angok for that.

28:35.046 --> 28:36.423
I do have one.

28:36.506 --> 28:37.757
Did you move here?

28:37.841 --> 28:38.800
Yes.

28:39.342 --> 28:40.969
He'll help you make one.

28:51.855 --> 28:53.064
By the way…

28:54.649 --> 28:56.985
Is your head okay from yesterday?

29:01.239 --> 29:02.490
I'm sorry.

29:04.659 --> 29:07.912
And thank you so much for the map.

29:13.001 --> 29:15.003
What's she talking about? What map?

29:15.086 --> 29:16.337
A map?

29:27.182 --> 29:28.516
Here you go.

29:31.144 --> 29:32.479
Isn't this the billiard club?

29:34.314 --> 29:36.149
You live there?

29:37.192 --> 29:39.110
-Yes.
-Right.

29:44.157 --> 29:45.825
Thank you.

29:48.745 --> 29:50.622
LIBRARY MEMBERSHIP CARD
LEE YEO-REUM

29:54.918 --> 29:56.127
What's with her?

29:56.211 --> 29:57.545
How could anyone live there?

30:01.800 --> 30:02.842
Hey.

30:37.544 --> 30:38.545
Excuse me.

30:39.128 --> 30:40.713
Your bag is over there.

30:40.797 --> 30:42.131
Actually…

30:46.094 --> 30:46.928
Look.

30:47.011 --> 30:50.014
This is my seat.
So don't sit here again, okay?

30:50.723 --> 30:53.434
Kim Bom. Keep your voice down.

30:53.518 --> 30:55.770
Why is she always picking on me?

31:07.240 --> 31:08.283
Excuse me.

31:24.257 --> 31:25.341
Hello?

31:25.884 --> 31:29.012
Can you come outside the library
for a second?

31:29.637 --> 31:32.056
-Who are you?
-You'll see when you come out.

31:32.682 --> 31:34.309
Who are you to tell me…

31:35.810 --> 31:36.936
Hello?

31:37.770 --> 31:39.188
Hey, Kim Bom.

31:39.272 --> 31:41.357
Are you serious? Take the call outside.

31:42.150 --> 31:43.568
Whatever.

31:59.292 --> 32:00.209
What do you want?

32:00.293 --> 32:03.338
I think our phones got mixed up.

32:03.421 --> 32:04.464
Sorry?

32:05.757 --> 32:06.758
Here.

32:10.803 --> 32:13.514
You must have confused them
because neither of us use a case.

32:16.684 --> 32:17.810
Grandmother, I assume?

32:18.770 --> 32:19.896
Do you mean me?

32:20.521 --> 32:22.106
Can't you tell I'm in high school?

32:23.691 --> 32:25.818
I mean the wallpaper on your phone.

32:28.738 --> 32:30.740
Why are you looking through my phone?

32:31.658 --> 32:32.617
I'm sorry.

32:32.700 --> 32:34.077
Mind your own business.

32:35.787 --> 32:36.829
Excuse me.

32:39.248 --> 32:40.375
What now?

32:43.670 --> 32:44.796
It's nothing.

32:53.096 --> 32:54.847
Whatever. Time to go eat.

32:57.183 --> 32:59.435
Here's your food. Enjoy.

33:00.186 --> 33:03.189
-Where were you? You came late.
-He was busy.

33:03.272 --> 33:04.691
-Goodness.
-Hey.

33:05.274 --> 33:06.192
What would you like to order?

33:08.027 --> 33:09.404
Hello.

33:10.780 --> 33:12.156
What do you want?

33:13.282 --> 33:15.159
Can I get a bowl of sundaeguk?

33:15.243 --> 33:18.162
-One sundaeguk!
-Okay.

33:19.080 --> 33:21.624
-Order's up.
-I'm coming!

33:25.837 --> 33:27.130
Enjoy.

33:39.308 --> 33:41.227
Can we get another bottle of soju?

33:41.811 --> 33:42.937
Okay!

33:43.021 --> 33:44.522
-Just one more.
-Gosh.

33:44.605 --> 33:46.774
-Should you be drinking this much?
-It's fine.

33:46.858 --> 33:48.443
Take a shot.

33:48.526 --> 33:51.863
-You should drink in moderation.
-It's fine.

33:51.946 --> 33:54.657
-I need the drink.
-The meat is delicious.

33:54.741 --> 33:59.120
All right, I'll live however I want here.
No more walking on eggshells.

33:59.203 --> 34:01.039
-The meat's really good, right?
-Ma'am.

34:01.122 --> 34:02.749
It's amazing.

34:02.832 --> 34:04.959
-I know, right?
-Ma'am.

34:05.043 --> 34:06.127
Cheers!

34:06.210 --> 34:08.463
Can I get a bottle of soju?

34:08.546 --> 34:10.798
Make sure you don't drive, okay?

34:10.882 --> 34:12.341
I got you.

34:12.425 --> 34:14.177
I didn't even drink that much.

34:14.260 --> 34:16.054
But it looks like you did.

34:16.137 --> 34:18.347
No. I'm sober.

34:25.396 --> 34:26.522
This feels amazing.

34:27.231 --> 34:29.317
Hot food and a cold drink.

34:29.400 --> 34:31.569
Who came up with this?

35:14.487 --> 35:16.030
This is a grown-up's meal.

35:18.199 --> 35:20.868
JEIL RESTAURANT

35:20.952 --> 35:23.663
-Thank you for the food.
-Thank you.

35:23.746 --> 35:26.249
Okay, I'll put it on your tabs.

35:26.332 --> 35:27.416
See you.

35:28.543 --> 35:29.710
Gosh.

35:41.639 --> 35:44.100
How can you not finish your fish cakes?

35:50.940 --> 35:52.817
So obnoxious.

36:02.660 --> 36:05.538
ANGOK PUBLIC LIBRARY

36:34.817 --> 36:36.694
Gosh, my head.

36:54.420 --> 36:56.547
How did I end up here?

36:59.926 --> 37:02.011
-Goodbye.
-Bye.

37:02.094 --> 37:04.555
-Thank you for the food.
-Sure.

37:05.056 --> 37:09.185
10 HOURS AGO

37:09.268 --> 37:11.604
Look how much she drank
so early in the day.

37:18.277 --> 37:19.320
Steal it.

37:23.157 --> 37:24.367
So close.

37:27.161 --> 37:28.579
Let's play again.

37:28.663 --> 37:30.498
-Where are you going?
-Dae-bum.

37:30.581 --> 37:32.750
What are you doing?

37:32.833 --> 37:35.169
Come back, Dae-bum.

38:05.700 --> 38:06.867
-Come on!
-Let's go!

38:06.951 --> 38:08.411
Try imitating her.

38:08.494 --> 38:10.746
Should I do it?

38:11.914 --> 38:14.333
-Hey, look at this.
-Let's play!

38:15.960 --> 38:19.463
-Rock, paper, scissors, shoot!
-Be quiet!

38:19.547 --> 38:21.173
Oh, whatever.

38:21.257 --> 38:23.092
-He's here!
-He's here!

38:23.175 --> 38:25.678
-I got you!
-What is that?

38:26.262 --> 38:27.471
Is she drunk?

38:27.555 --> 38:29.598
-She's lying down.
-She fell.

38:29.682 --> 38:30.808
She fell.

38:31.767 --> 38:33.269
-What is this?
-Look.

38:33.352 --> 38:35.354
-Hey, it's like a snake!
-The alcohol must have

38:35.438 --> 38:38.024
-gotten to her hair.
-It must have!

38:38.107 --> 38:39.191
Excuse me.

38:39.275 --> 38:40.985
What do you think you're doing?

38:41.068 --> 38:43.612
-That's Medusa, not a snake.
-Right, Medusa.

38:43.696 --> 38:45.865
-The alcohol must have gotten to her hair.
-Is she out of her mind?

38:45.948 --> 38:47.658
I think she might be.

38:47.742 --> 38:49.744
Oh, I'm at the library.

38:49.827 --> 38:51.579
-What's wrong with her?
-Hey.

38:51.662 --> 38:53.414
-It's because she's drunk.
-Why is she at the library?

38:53.497 --> 38:55.166
-I know.
-I have to go home.

38:55.916 --> 38:58.669
-She's moving!
-Move aside now.

38:58.753 --> 39:01.130
You shouldn't be coming here drunk.

39:02.006 --> 39:03.299
I'm sorry.

39:03.382 --> 39:04.425
I accept your apology.

39:05.634 --> 39:08.429
-Push her down more!
-Come on, kids. Move now.

39:08.512 --> 39:10.431
-Let's go!
-Come on!

39:10.514 --> 39:11.390
ARCHIVES

39:11.474 --> 39:13.017
Don't go in there!

39:13.100 --> 39:15.144
-Let's go!
-Not in there!

39:15.227 --> 39:16.520
Hey, Dae-bum!

39:16.604 --> 39:18.814
I have to go home.

39:19.899 --> 39:21.692
I have to go home.

39:21.776 --> 39:23.319
-Guys, come here!
-What's this?

39:24.945 --> 39:26.280
I must be out of my mind.

39:27.323 --> 39:29.241
I should go home now.

39:32.328 --> 39:33.746
What's this?

39:38.667 --> 39:40.461
Gosh, what time is it?

39:43.339 --> 39:44.548
It's 3 a.m.?

39:53.307 --> 39:54.350
Excuse me!

39:56.310 --> 39:59.188
I'm still in the library!
Please open the door!

39:59.271 --> 40:01.482
Please. What do I do?

40:04.026 --> 40:05.111
My phone.

40:14.995 --> 40:17.289
Don't come near me.

40:17.790 --> 40:20.376
Stop! Don't come near me!

40:25.673 --> 40:26.924
Mr. Librarian?

40:34.557 --> 40:35.766
Thank you.

40:51.115 --> 40:55.077
But why are you here this late?

40:57.872 --> 40:59.540
Did you stay because of me?

41:01.041 --> 41:02.168
I'm so sorry.

41:10.009 --> 41:12.428
You must be sober now.

41:12.511 --> 41:16.765
The power will be back up
at eight in the morning,

41:16.849 --> 41:18.267
and the door opens.

41:19.018 --> 41:21.520
Feel free to rest
wherever you want until then.

41:23.272 --> 41:26.484
I see. He must be mute.

41:28.277 --> 41:29.403
But…

41:30.446 --> 41:33.032
why didn't you wake me up?

41:36.869 --> 41:38.913
I'll be going, Dae-bum.

41:38.996 --> 41:40.664
Wrap up and go home, okay?

41:40.748 --> 41:41.832
See you.

41:41.916 --> 41:43.042
7 HOURS AGO

41:45.377 --> 41:46.420
Bye.

42:58.325 --> 43:00.035
I guess you tried to wake me up.

43:01.954 --> 43:03.539
You should get some sleep.

43:24.768 --> 43:27.104
If you want to do some reading,

43:27.187 --> 43:30.024
go to the very right side of the windows.

43:30.107 --> 43:32.151
It's the brightest there.

43:34.653 --> 43:36.071
Thank you.

43:53.881 --> 43:54.965
This…

44:00.679 --> 44:01.847
Excuse me.

44:03.515 --> 44:04.600
Are you in here?

44:11.899 --> 44:12.983
Mr. Librarian.

44:15.069 --> 44:16.278
Mr. Librarian.

44:17.780 --> 44:20.032
I think you can stop rolling away.

44:24.620 --> 44:27.498
I just wanted to return this to you.

44:31.418 --> 44:33.712
But I guess…

44:37.758 --> 44:42.262
I'll use it for the night
and give it back to you in the morning.

44:46.642 --> 44:48.102
Have a good night.

44:51.814 --> 44:53.107
Also…

44:54.483 --> 44:57.486
Where is the bathroom?

45:08.038 --> 45:10.874
The bathroom is outside.

45:13.001 --> 45:16.880
Why did he give me water
when the bathroom is outside?

45:18.298 --> 45:20.467
He didn't drink any.
I'm the only one who drank.

45:21.093 --> 45:23.887
No. I shouldn't think about it.

45:23.971 --> 45:26.390
Just don't think about
wanting to go to the bathroom.

45:27.141 --> 45:28.225
Darn it.

46:02.551 --> 46:04.052
It's almost time.

46:05.429 --> 46:06.972
Almost time.

46:09.099 --> 46:10.559
Hold it a little bit more.

46:15.731 --> 46:17.608
A little bit more.

46:20.444 --> 46:21.445
Please.

46:33.624 --> 46:36.084
I can't let my guard down
at the last minute.

46:36.627 --> 46:38.337
I must not run.

46:38.879 --> 46:41.173
Once it starts coming out,
I won't be able to…

47:32.808 --> 47:34.351
Goodbye.

47:51.076 --> 47:55.831
ANGOK PUBLIC LIBRARY

48:21.607 --> 48:23.150
My goodness.

48:24.067 --> 48:25.819
-What's happening?
-Excuse me.

48:27.362 --> 48:28.488
What is he doing?

48:29.323 --> 48:30.657
Your bag.

48:36.538 --> 48:38.332
Right. My bag.

48:41.251 --> 48:42.502
Wait a second.

48:43.170 --> 48:44.588
Did he just talk?

48:45.088 --> 48:47.174
So he can talk?

48:50.177 --> 48:51.970
Dae-bum, what was that?

48:52.638 --> 48:53.680
Tell me.

49:06.193 --> 49:10.280
How drunk do you have to be
to fall asleep at the library?

49:10.364 --> 49:11.281
Right?

49:11.782 --> 49:14.117
You're a weirdo too.
You could have just left her here.

49:14.201 --> 49:15.702
Why spend the night here with her?

49:16.662 --> 49:18.622
You can't even talk
when there's a stranger around.

49:21.291 --> 49:22.292
Hey.

49:23.293 --> 49:25.545
Go take a shower. Take this home too.

49:27.297 --> 49:29.675
Mom packed you some ginseng
and some other stuff.

49:30.759 --> 49:32.886
I haven't finished
the ones she sent before.

49:32.969 --> 49:36.014
She's just trying to win you over.
Give her a call.

49:36.098 --> 49:37.349
I think she's upset.

49:38.100 --> 49:40.310
Tell her I said thank you.

49:40.394 --> 49:41.603
All right.

49:41.687 --> 49:43.939
-Make sure you do.
-Got it.

49:48.443 --> 49:49.778
Did he hear it?

49:51.571 --> 49:52.948
He must have, right?

49:53.490 --> 49:56.535
Of course, he did. I'm so embarrassed.

49:57.869 --> 50:01.665
What am I going to do?
This is humiliating.

50:13.969 --> 50:16.054
So embarrassing.

50:31.570 --> 50:35.198
Okay, I have nothing more to lose.

50:36.158 --> 50:39.703
I'll live a life that I won't regret.

50:41.538 --> 50:43.290
I can do it!

50:46.418 --> 50:47.711
I can do it.

51:39.679 --> 51:42.557
That lady is renting out the billiard club
at only 50,000 won a month.

51:42.641 --> 51:43.683
Isn't that ridiculous?

51:43.767 --> 51:45.519
The water pipe is leaking.

51:45.602 --> 51:48.146
I thought I told you
to take care of it yourself.

51:48.230 --> 51:50.106
-First, you sleep here,
-Oh, no.

51:50.190 --> 51:51.233
and now you damage books.

51:51.316 --> 51:52.609
What a catastrophe.

51:53.860 --> 51:56.446
Not a soul in this town likes you.

51:56.530 --> 51:58.198
So behave yourself.

51:58.281 --> 52:00.075
Don't think of staying here long.

52:00.158 --> 52:01.535
It'd be better if you'd leave.

52:01.618 --> 52:04.037
Such a big nuisance came into town.

52:04.120 --> 52:06.998
Let's give her back the money
and kick her out.

52:07.499 --> 52:10.627
Subtitle translation by: Jea-Heon Chung
